# 👨‍🏫 Mentor's Note

You're no longer just building an app—you are building a **healthcare product**.

One thing I want you to keep in mind as you continue:

> **Our app should help users understand their reports, not diagnose medical conditions.**

That's an important distinction. The app can explain what a value means, show trends over time, and encourage users to consult a healthcare professional when appropriate, but it should avoid making definitive medical diagnoses.

That approach builds credibility and aligns well with the role you want the product to play.

